.TH "drm_gem_cma_get_sg_table" 9 "drm_gem_cma_get_sg_table" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
drm_gem_cma_get_sg_table \- provide a scatter/gather table of pinned pages for a CMA GEM object
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "struct sg_table *" drm_gem_cma_get_sg_table
.BI "(struct drm_gem_object *obj "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "obj" 12
GEM object
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This function exports a scatter/gather table by
calling the standard DMA mapping API. Drivers using the CMA helpers should
set this as their \fIdrm_gem_object_funcs.get_sg_table\fP callback.
.SH "RETURN"
A pointer to the scatter/gather table of pinned pages or NULL on failure.
